LOMBOK:
 need to be installed in a library.so we use pom.mxl
 BROWSER:
  search "lombok maven dependency" in google
  click org.projectlombok >> lombok-Maven Repository
  click latest version on the top left corner
  their wil be maven,gradle,svt,grape..........
  click Mavencopy the code.
